file.name: issue_9848.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: OpenAPI Petstore
  description: "sample spec"
  license:
    name: Apache-2.0
    url: https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://petstore.swagger.io:80/v2
tags:
  - name: isX
    description: an api that ensures that isX properties are present on Schema classes
paths:
  /uniqueTypes:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 'unique array'
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/uniqueArray'
  /nonUniqueTypes:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 'non-unique array'
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/nonUniqueArray'
components:
  schemas:
    uniqueArray:
      type: object
      properties:
        array:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
          uniqueItems: true
    nonUniqueArray:
      type: object
      properties:
        array:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
          uniqueItems: false
